name: Do Narwhals Dream of Electric Tea?

metadata.name: Narwhal #1
metadata.description:
Another thing that got forgotten was the fact that, against all probability, a narwhal had suddenly been called into existence, in a rather peculiar location for a narwhal.

And since this is not a naturally tenable position for a narwhal, this poor innocent creature had very little time to come to terms with its identity as a narwhal before it then had to come to terms with not being a narwhal anymore...

'Do Narwhals Dream of Electric Tea' is a generative art project from the mind of @Waxbones, powered by @Props
